VFelicitating  P. Suseela
p3
sVnews
p4
VThe highlight of the event being organised by Callezee (Ph: 25555555) and Callchennai (Ph: 24444444) will be the felicitation to P. Suseela on the conferment of Padma Bhushan on her. K.J.Yesudas will do the honours.On the occasion, Vijaya Chamundeshwari, daughter of Gemini Ganesh and Savithri will be honoured in memory of her parents.The programme will be anchored by Y. Gee. Mahendra and ARS.The singers on the show include Kalpana, Prasanna, Saindhavi, Madhuvanthi Arun, Kovai Murali, S.N. Surendar, Ananthu, Raja and Madhumita.Connoisseurs may call the above mentioned numbers for passes.
